reviewText: Both the Dora and Bubble Guppy are brand new you us and great!  I like the variety and getting to experience a single episode of something new, without investing in a full dvd.  We do not have cable and the kids watch exclusively PBS and DVDs that I approve.  Kids are 2 & 3:)
This is helped my son so much with kindness
Good price on a good kids DVD.

My son loves the lets learn series! I am super happy with these dvds! Learning with friends is the best. I love this DVD actually teachs about kindness and it helps keep my toddlers attention because it is his favorite characters or as he calls it, His friends
This DVD has all my daughters favorite shows and she loves watching it. We have many Nick Jr dad's like this and love all them!

I think learning the importance of Kindness is easier when it's taught by a child's favorite characters. I mostly purchased this for my 4 year old because of the variety of favorite characters and shows, but the subject of kindness is an added bonus. We instill kindness in our children from a young age, but sometimes it's home a little easier when they are seeing their favorite characters on the screen displaying kindness.

Very cute and perfect for my almost 3 and almost 4 yr olds. Less advanced than the 123, ABC, and Colors DVD. This has cuter shows than I usually see from these series. Dragon-Princess theme for Dora and Bubble Guppies. Probably the least annoying toddler DVD I've purchased, and my oldest is 16! Super cute coloring page on the back of DVD insert page.
Great dvd for our collection. We do not have cable so these mix dvds are awesome!
